# --- Model weights & large inference assets ---
# YuNet (~230 KiB) may be vendored or auto-downloaded; allow only this ONNX name.
# Tracked inference (fresh clone): gesture, HaGRID YOLO hands, YuNet ONNX, MediaPipe hand landmarker.
# Other *.pt / *.task (HF fallbacks, backups, last.pt, training outputs) stay ignored.
*.pt
!gesture_drone/models/gesture_model.pt
!gesture_drone/models/yolo_hands/weights/best.pt
*.pth
*.onnx
!gesture_drone/models/face_detection_yunet_2023mar.onnx
*.engine
*.task
!gesture_drone/models/hand_landmarker.task
*.safetensors
*.bin
*.ckpt

